= Version 1.2.0

  * Add UTF-8 encoding string to spec files
  * Amend description to refer to Crossroads I/O as a messaging library
  * XS::Util is now a singleton class
  * Util.error_check method is now public
  * Handle return codes from xs_connect and xs_bind that are > 0 or < -1
  
= Version 1.1.0

  * Version number bumped to reflect addition of new features in v1.0.1
  * Removed unused 'init_option?' method in socket.rb

= Version 1.0.1

  * Re-working of some ZeroMQ examples for use with Crossroads I/O
  * Addition of missing socket option XS::IPV4ONLY
  * Addition of new socket option XS::KEEPALIVE
  * Editing of inline comments for Yard documentation in Textile
  * Amended .gemspec to exclude ext/libxs.so from build to accommodate Travis CI in development

= Version 1.0.0

  * Initial release
